name: DartCheckoutHelper
0:
”Alexa, ask checkout helper 170”
”Alexa, ask checkout helper how to finish 40”
”Alexa, ask checkout helper for 100”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: checkout helper
des: This skill will give you the darts to throw to finish your darts game with a double. Any score between 40 and 170 which is finish-able with 3 darts will give a correct finish. If you miss one, just ask again for the new score.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
